FBIS3-20359 "drweu061_k_94002" FBIS-WEU-94-061 Document Type:Daily Report 28 Mar 1994 PORTUGAL New Navy Chief of Staff Sworn In LD2803203594 Lisbon RTP Internacional Television in Portuguese 1800 GMT 28 Mar 94 LD2803203594 Lisbon RTP Internacional Television Language: Portuguese Article Type:BFN [Text] The Portuguese Navy has a new chief of staff. Admiral Ribeiro Pacheco was sworn in today, defending the need for further submarine acquisition. Ribeiro Pacheco stated that the three submarines in operation in the Portuguese Navy are reaching the end of their life span.
